</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="41792" d="5973" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčThen, what would be the opposite word of "loneliness"?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="47765" d="5705" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčIf someone is thinking of me... would that be "love"?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="47765" d="5705" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčIf someone is thinking of me... would that be "love"?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="53470" d="5573" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčToday again, I halt my steps alone in the future that's being born‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="53470" d="5573" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčToday again, I halt my steps alone in the future that's being born‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="59043" d="4938" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčA rain that never falls, closing my eyes‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="59043" d="4938" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčA rain that never falls, closing my eyes‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="63981" d="5639" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčNo matter how much I cry, no matter how much I cry, it's still goodbye‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="63981" d="5639" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčNo matter how much I cry, no matter how much I cry, it's still goodbye‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="69620" d="6706" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčTo you, fading into the twilight, I say, "Thank you."‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="69620" d="6706" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčTo you, fading into the twilight, I say, "Thank you."‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="76326" d="4638" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčLet's cherish each other for eternity‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="76326" d="4638" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčLet's cherish each other for eternity‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="80964" d="3504" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčShall we pinky swear? You can make that promise‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="80964" d="3504" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčShall we pinky swear? You can make that promise‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="84468" d="2169" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčBecause we will surely...‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="84468" d="2169" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčBecause we will surely...‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="86637" d="6106" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčI want to see you, I want to see you, let's meet here again‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="86637" d="6106" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčI want to see you, I want to see you, let's meet here again‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="92743" d="5806" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčA promise is a ticket to the future, right? You'll board it, won't you?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="92743" d="5806" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčA promise is a ticket to the future, right? You'll board it, won't you?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="98549" d="4938" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčAt the final stop, your dream awaits-‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="98549" d="4938" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčAt the final stop, your dream awaits-‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="103487" d="3604" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe stars blur in the sky I look up to‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="103487" d="3604" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe stars blur in the sky I look up to‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="107091" d="2802" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe scent of tears, ah...‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="107091" d="2802" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč<